      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAROS JOURNEY (1) made a big impression on debut when flew the lids from out wide with a slick turn of foot, going on to clock 17.42 in a 5 length win over 300m at this track. Promising type who will be in this for a long way. HELL BENT (8) is having his first start around this circuit. In the money last start when third (25.01) at Sale over 435m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Expected to feature again. CLOUD KEEPING (2) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Little Ditzy (23.34) in a Novice race. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. UNHOOKED (4) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
